// How Java program works?
Package -> Class -> Method -> Statements (;)
Source Code - src
Byte Code - out Folder
Bytece Code - (java) ->(JVM) - Memory(RAM) -> Native Code.
Main Method public static void main(String[]) - **JVM start the execution**


